%p.intro The <em>easy</em> way to send <em>personalized</em> greeting cards to your <em>friends</em> and <em>family</em> online. You won't find any silly music, animations or adverts here - just <em>great looking</em> e-cards!

%p.intro <strong>Click on a card to get started!</strong>

%section.cards
  %h1.category Birthday Cards
  %ul
    - @birthday.each do |design|
      %li
        %a.card(href='/card/#{design.id}')
          %h1.title{:class => design.name}= design.title
          %img.reflect{:src=>settings.images + "/" + design.image + "-th.png",:alt => design.alt, :width => 128, :height => 84}

